| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6583 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a805cf8e-ffc2-5f7b-bd0e-77f7cc77f5f5"
